title: DTO
description: This is a randomly ordered feed of the most recent entries from DTO, skipping any feeds with errors.

items.title: U.S. goods trade deficit narrowed significantly in April

items.description: The U.S. and China in mid-May agreed to a 90-day suspension on most tariffs after Trump slapped sky-high tariffs on the big U.S. trade partner.

items.title: Fed-favored PCE gauge shows tame April inflation. Trade wars remain a wild card.

items.description: Three judges — including a Trump appointee — on a federal trade court had invalidated all of Trump's "reciprocal" tariffs and other duties.
